# Privacy Policy

Your privacy is important to us. This app collects minimal data necessary to function, such as creature names and organ configurations submitted via the form. It will also send your public reddit username. This data is used solely for simulation and display purposes.

Username is only sent for scoring purposes, and to display cosmetics

We do not sell or share your data with third parties.

Data may be temporarily stored on our servers to support real-time updates.

If you have any concerns, please contact me at r.tait64@protonmail.com